    <briefdescription>
<para>Unidirectional forward-only motor controller (e.g., aircraft ESC, throttle). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Maps input range 0..1000 to driver output. Negative inputs are treated as stop (0).</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Driver</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Driver class (must implement actUnipolar(unsigned short)) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>kMinValue</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Minimum output value (e.g., 20 = stop) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>kMaxValue</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Maximum output value (e.g., 1000 = full throttle) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
